commit.message:
Final Release of v. 1.1.0 GroupAlarm

Fixed many bugs and added new features.

Fixed deleting alarms.

Fixed a lot of bugs, now need to work on fixing the share feature.

Tried changing some of the delete function.

Delete still not working, but working better than before. Updated some forgot password, sharing, etc.

New Icon and features added.

Notifications show up in-app, sharing notifications work, and added a new and better icon.

Final MVP

Created the Final MVP

Sharing in works.

The sharing feature is almost done. Just need to reference some stuff from firebase and should be good to go!

Fixed some editing errors

Fixed errors related to the repeat days for the alarm.

Fixed crash

Fixed a crash issue due to mislabeling in storyboard.

Added more support for editing.

Displays editing properties correctly.

Added more support for editing alarms

Can now see same time in picker view as time of alarm being edited. Same for repeated days and label.

Upload array to firebase

Uploaded repeated days array to firebase.

Updates to Login and Firebase

Made a better login flow and alarms retain from firebase data after app is closed.
Able to add alarms to cells
